[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0132","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0132.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0468","title":"Microsoft Internet Explorer 任意文件读取漏洞","description":"Internet Explorer 5.0 的 Microsoft Scriptlet 组件存在信息泄露漏洞，远程攻击者可诱导用户访问恶意网页，利用该组件绕过浏览器安全限制，读取客户端文件系统中的任意文件内容。该漏洞影响 Windows 平台上安装的 IE 5.0 版本，攻击者无需身份认证即可实施攻击，危害等级高，可能导致敏感信息（如本地文件内容）被窃取。","severity":"HIGH","score":8.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0468"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-04-09T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:27.557","remediation":"立即安装 Microsoft 安全公告 MS99-012 提供的 MSHTML.DLL 更新补丁，将 Internet Explorer 升级至已修复版本。该补丁通过更新 MSHTML 解析引擎阻止恶意脚本自动粘贴文件名到文件上传控件，防止文件被未经用户确认即提交至远程服务器。如无法安装补丁，可禁用 ActiveX 控件和脚本功能作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1999/ms99-012","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ad01ef67b360e9139b8072c8e614b7c7c1f658d2/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0468.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0468","https://github.com/cisagov/vulnrichment/blob/3df4338205b90ec907c1a337dd4fb689267150e3/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0468.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0468.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/18de81c56daca1c9e33223f0b95bdb8312a1ca75/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-qx62-xr98-6mvc/GHSA-qx62-xr98-6mvc.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/1d279cde1e5f7d9e150ca373126c9b35476ad3f5/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0468.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--c11e9e7e-dc7b-4919-ae86-b7ac71c65565.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000602.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0132.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0132.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0019","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0019.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0287","title":"WebCom datakommunikation Guestbook rguest.exe 任意文件访问漏洞","description":"WebCom datakommunikation Guestbook 0.1 的 rguest.exe CGI 程序存在任意文件访问漏洞。远程攻击者无需认证即可通过向该 CGI 程序发送特制请求，利用路径遍历技术读取 Web 服务器上的任意文件，导致敏感信息泄露。该漏洞影响 Guestbook 0.1 版本，攻击条件低、利用简单，危害较大。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0287"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-04-09T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:04.593","remediation":"立即从 Web 服务器 CGI 目录中删除或重命名 rguest.exe 和 wguest.exe 文件，彻底禁用该留言本组件。在 IIS 中可通过「应用程序配置」移除该脚本映射，或在文件系统层面撤销 IUSR_MACHINENAME 账户对 CGI 目录的执行权限。建议替换为其他仍在维护的开源留言本或使用无文件写入的第三方评论服务（如 Disqus）以彻底消除风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://marc.info/?l=ntbugtraq&m=92368828704896&w=2","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/1421f0a4349d5d46275cadd9c7c62349edf9c8bb/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0287.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0287","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0287.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0287.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2f876a2c24d5ccd5bbd081f09e801e580536456a/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0287.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0287.json","https://github.com/magicsword-io/Magic-SigExplorer/blob/2c28b91b003429a144a687199ee99ebd26f1a343/Magic-SigExplorer/docs/cve_report.md","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153400_153500.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0019.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1007","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1007.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1196","title":"Hummingbird Exceed 5.0 远程拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Hummingbird Exceed 5.0 X Window 服务器存在输入验证缺陷，远程攻击者可通过向 TCP 端口 6000 发送特制的畸形数据，触发服务端解析异常，导致 X 服务进程崩溃或资源耗尽，造成拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 Hummingbird Exceed 5.0 版本，攻击无需认证，仅需网络可达即可实施。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1196"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-04-07T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:55.377","remediation":"将 Hummingbird Exceed 从 5.0 版本升级至 6.0.1、6.0.2 或 6.1 版本以修复该拒绝服务漏洞。如无法立即升级，可在防火墙或主机层面限制对 TCP 端口 6000（X11 服务端口）的外部访问，仅允许可信 IP 连接，作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/13451","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/158","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/4e8d44fc9434dcaf08511a3267e0bf049a6756de/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1196.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1196","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/470a5f1c0d1bd36cd0a6327cda49cf96a1474588/content/CVE-1999-1196.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/f9199c6ea2112c9d2536a126688b640a45f0982a/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1196.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/4544d3857250fe21711ce8febf38e8822729678f/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-g5v2-hv74-hhp6/GHSA-g5v2-hv74-hhp6.json","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/R/random_crap_DoS.nasl","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Exploit-List-Ja/blob/b82432e7d59d95db9f183c0cefa7744595784afa/1999.tsv","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/39f1db26eec9899ab2f8110ab3b45424c6fe9ec2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1196.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000601.txt","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--42baa4ee-b6bc-4f5a-9835-e12a18e09f85.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1007.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0139","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0139.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0473","title":"Rsync rsync 目录权限非预期修改漏洞","description":"rsync 2.3.1 之前版本存在权限处理缺陷，在文件传输过程中服务端目录权限可能被错误地应用到客户端工作目录。攻击者可通过构造特定权限的共享目录，诱使客户端执行 rsync 同步操作后，导致客户端工作目录的权限被非预期修改，可能造成信息泄露或权限提升。该漏洞影响广泛使用的 rsync 工具各早期版本，建议升级至 2.3.1 及以上版本修复。","severity":"LOW","score":2.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0473"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-04-07T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:28.367","remediation":"升级 rsync 至 2.3.1 或更高版本，该版本修复了同步过程中权限被意外修改的问题。如无法升级，避免在不受信任的目录上执行 rsync 拉取操作，并在传输后手动检查并重置工作目录权限。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/145"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0139.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0138","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0138.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0472","title":"NetApp NetCache SNMP 默认团体名安全绕过漏洞","description":"NetApp C630 Netcache 设备中存在 SNMP 默认团体字符串安全配置漏洞。管理员尝试禁用默认的 \"public\" 团体字符串后，该字符串仍未被正确移除，导致攻击者可通过 SNMP 协议利用默认团体字符串远程访问设备，获取系统敏感信息。该漏洞影响 NetApp C630 Netcache 设备，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中危。建议管理员手动确认并彻底删除默认团体字符串配置。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0472"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-04-07T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:28.237","remediation":"立即检查 NetApp NetCache C630 设备上的 SNMP 配置，确认默认 community string \"public\" 是否已被禁用或修改为自定义复杂字符串。由于该产品已停止支持且无官方补丁，建议在设备 ACL 中限制 SNMP（UDP 161/162）仅允许受信任管理 IP 访问，或直接禁用 SNMP 服务。对于仍在运行的旧设备，应尽快迁移至受支持的替代产品。在 Brocade 等后续受影响产品中，升级至厂商确认不受影响的固件版本。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0472","https://www.broadcom.com/support/fibre-channel-networking/security-advisories/brocade-security-advisory-2017-240","https://www.broadcom.com/support/fibre-channel-networking/security-advisories/brocade-security-advisory-2017-240/"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0138.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1021","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1021.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1245","title":"ucd-snmp SNMP 服务默认公共团体字符串信息泄露漏洞","description":"ucd-snmp 服务器 3.52 版本中存在信息泄露漏洞，其 vacm 模块未能正确禁用对 public 团体字符串的访问权限。远程攻击者可利用 SNMP 协议的默认团体字符串直接查询目标设备，获取系统配置、网络拓扑、运行进程等敏感信息，导致信息泄露。该漏洞影响 ucd-snmp 3.52 版本，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中危。建议升级至更高版本或修改 SNMP 团体字符串配置以缓解风险。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1245"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-04-06T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:01.670","remediation":"升级 ucd-snmp 至 4.0 以上版本，或迁移至其继承项目 net-snmp。在 snmpd.conf 中将 `com2sec` 的 public community 改为自定义字符串或使用 `rocommunity` 指定仅允许特定源 IP 访问，同时在防火墙层面限制 UDP 161 端口的入站流量。如无法升级，将 `community` 指令注释掉并使用 `rocommunity` 替代。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/2086","htt