99-0610"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-04-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:43.933","remediation":"升级 Webcart CGI 程序至厂商修复版本（1999 年后发布的安全版本），并在 Web 服务器配置中将 Webcart CGI 脚本的执行权限收紧为仅限授权用户访问，移除或重命名暴露内部数据的脚本路径。同时在 Web 服务器（如 Apache）中禁用目录列表、限制 CGI 目录访问来源 IP，并审查 CGI 配置文件确保不输出私有信息作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-17T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=92462991805485&w=2","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/5a67adc3536b9edff12a57c2de9cd5aa5d12653d/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0610.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0610","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/e046e4965f64348bd29a0c62edd023b3c580939e/content/CVE-1999-0610.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2853180ecaf9d7461fd6bb98e4528ce223cae51d/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0610.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/2e86ccb45bad26f6ff984e676f6d08b925d0e6ee/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-pcwm-fmqp-52qw/GHSA-pcwm-fmqp-52qw.json","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/W/webcart.nasl","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/178b809924783e13787d17bb1b1fd55ad3b8639b/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0610.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153400_153500.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0183.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0183.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0183.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0177","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0177.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0606","title":"EZMall 2000 购物车 CGI 程序配置错误敏感信息泄露漏洞","description":"EZMall 2000 购物车 CGI 程序 \"mall2000.cgi\" 存在错误配置漏洞，未经身份认证的远程攻击者无需任何凭据即可通过网络直接访问该 CGI 程序，导致程序错误地泄露敏感私有信息。该漏洞影响部署 EZMall 2000 网上购物系统的 Web 服务器，攻击者只需向目标服务器发送特制的 HTTP 请求即可触发信息泄露，可能暴露客户订单详情、个人隐私数据等敏感内容。根据 NVD 记录，CVSS v2 评分为 5.0（中危），弱点类型为 CWE-200（向未授权方泄露敏感信息）。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0606"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-04-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:43.457","remediation":"升级 EZMall 2000 购物车程序至官方修复版本，删除或限制对存在配置缺陷的 CGI 脚本 mall2000.cgi 的公开访问权限。正确配置 Web 服务器目录及文件权限，禁止匿名用户读取包含私密信息的配置文件、订单数据和用户资料。可通过 .htaccess 或服务器规则限制 /cgi-bin/ 目录访问，并在防火墙层面对管理接口做 IP 白名单限制。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-17T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=92462991805485&w=2","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/64fd197c5b8f3e4f9493cb07798bdca54583505c/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0606.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0606","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/e046e4965f64348bd29a0c62edd023b3c580939e/content/CVE-1999-0606.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/9e7373a0dc9acbc4f26666870ca31dd641df9b83/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0606.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/2e86ccb45bad26f6ff984e676f6d08b925d0e6ee/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-r299-gjv8-v58g/GHSA-r299-gjv8-v58g.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0606.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153400_153500.json","https://github.com/InfoSecWarrior/Vulnerable-Box-Resources/blob/c784bcf63e1ec5c3a0116043d8653d00f0a21a0b/Vulnhub/OZ/oz-1-nikto-80-output.txt","https://github.com/hungryfoolou/Vulnerability_Mining/blob/3df1d8ed0489ae1228f975ae1f58a690aae53886/craw/cveid_craw/cveid_craw/data/cveid_by_kind/cveid_infor.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0177.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0177.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0177.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0176","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0176.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0605","title":"Order Form 1.0 购物车 CGI 程序信息泄露漏洞","description":"CVE-1999-0605 涉及 Order Form 1.0 购物车 CGI 程序的不正确配置漏洞。该程序在部署时若未正确设置访问权限或参数校验，可能导致服务器将本应保密的订单信息（如客户姓名、联系方式、支付相关数据等）通过 Web 接口直接暴露给未经身份认证的远程攻击者。攻击者可利用浏览器或简单 HTTP 请求访问该程序对应的 CGI 路径，从而获取存储在系统中的私有商业信息，造成敏感数据泄露。该漏洞影响所有使用 Order Form 1.0 购物车 CGI 且配置不当的网站，无需特殊权限即可利用。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0605"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-04-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:43.337","remediation":"将 Order Form 1.0 的订单数据存储目录移至 Web 服务器文档根目录之外，或通过 Web 服务器配置文件（如 Apache 的 `.htaccess` 或 Nginx 配置）禁止对订单目录的 Web 访问；同时将目录文件权限收紧为仅允许 Web 服务器用户读取（如设置为 640 或 600），删除已在文档树中暴露的订单文件，并通过搜索引擎站长平台提交删除请求以清除已收录的敏感数据。因 Order Form 1.0 已停止维护且存在设计缺陷，强烈建议迁移到经过安全审计的现代购物车程序，并对所有受影响客户进行数据泄露告知与信用卡监控。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-17T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=92462991805485&w=2","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/64fd197c5b8f3e4f9493cb07798bdca54583505c/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0605.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0605","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/e046e4965f64348bd29a0c62edd023b3c580939e/content/CVE-1999-0605.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/f71c1815da5fc1872d1d999eebe8b28a9e3854c7/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0605.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/2e86ccb45bad26f6ff984e676f6d08b925d0e6ee/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-vhcv-cv27-25rw/GHSA-vhcv-cv27-25rw.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0605.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x3000/2021/info.html","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/Yuning-J/VulnerabilityClassifier/blob/c0f06c21b73c26b5ee2b75c21a498eb04eada4b5/threatPrediction/cveIDThreatType/cve_idinfor"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0176.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0176.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0176.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0168","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0168.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0443","title":"BMC Patrol 管理软件重放攻击漏洞","description":"BMC Patrol 管理软件存在认证会话重放漏洞，远程攻击者无需身份认证即可通过网络捕获并重放有效的管理员认证数据包，从而获取管理员密码并完全控制受影响的 Patrol 管理控制台。该漏洞源于会话令牌缺乏时间戳或一次性使用机制，攻击者只需具备网络监听能力即可实施攻击，CVSS v2.0 评分为 10.0，危害等级严重。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0443"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-04-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:24.467","remediation":"升级 BMC Patrol 至 3.2 及以上版本，该版本修复了认证会话中缺少随机数（nonce）机制的问题，可有效防止重放攻击。如无法升级，应在网络层面限制 Patrol Agent 管理端口（默认 3181/TCP）的访问来源，仅允许受信任管理 IP 连接，并启用 Patrol 的 SSL/TLS 加密通信功能。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/13204"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0168.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0153","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0153.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0480","title":"GNU Midnight Commander 符号链接攻击拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Midnight Commander 4.x 版本存在符号链接（symlink）攻击漏洞。本地攻击者可通过在当前目录下创建恶意符号链接，诱使 Midnight Commander 在处理文件列表时错误地跟随该链接，导致程序崩溃或资源耗尽，造成拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 Midnight Commander 4.x 系列版本，CVSS 评分 2.1，危害等级低，利用前提是攻击者拥有本地访问权限。","severity":"LOW","score":2.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0480"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-04-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:29.260","remediation":"升级 Midnight Commander 至 4.5.50 及以上版本，该版本修复了符号链接竞争条件问题。如无法升级，可通过 `mc --no-subshell` 启动以降低攻击面，并避免在不可信目录中使用 MC 的文件管理功能。在系统层面，可将 `/tmp` 挂载为 `noexec`、`nodev`、`nosuid` 以限制本地攻击者的提权路径。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0480"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0153.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0133","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0133.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0469","title":"Microsoft Internet Explorer 窗口欺骗漏洞","description":"Internet Explorer 5.0 存在窗口欺骗漏洞，远程攻击者可通过构造恶意网页，利用浏览器窗口地址栏与内容区域显示不一致的缺陷，伪装成合法网站诱导用户访问。当用户浏览攻击者控制的页面时，浏览器地址栏可显示为受信任域名，而实际内容区域加载的是恶意页面，导致用户误信并输入敏感信息（如账号密码、信用卡号等），造成信息泄露。该漏洞影响 Windows 平台上 Internet Explorer 5.0 及早期版本，攻击条件低，仅需用户点击恶意链接即可触发。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0469"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-04-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:27.857","remediation":"立即升级至 Internet Explorer 5.01 Service Pack 2 或更高版本，该漏洞已在 IE 5.01 SP2 中修复。对于仍使用 IE 的旧系统，建议禁用 Active Scripting 功能并启用 Internet 区域安全级别为「高」，同时考虑迁移至现代浏览器（如 Edge/Chrome）以彻底规避风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0469","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ad01ef67b360e9139b8072c8e614b7c7c1f658d2/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0469.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0469","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0469.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/1d279cde1e5f7d9e150ca373126c9b35476ad3f5/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0469.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/18de81c56daca1c9e33223f0b95bdb8312a1ca75/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-3pmw-j7vc-7gww/GHSA-3pmw-j7vc-7gww.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0469.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x83000/82851/info.html","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000590.txt","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--068ab4eb-23e0-450f-9ef2-37fd804f7644.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0133.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0133.toml"}]